Text: Tira error al abrir instalador y no abre...
Installer doesn´t work. I´ve downloaded trial version from web site but serials aren´t good at all!

If you have problems this worked for me:
Right click "Trapcode Suite 12.0.0 Installer"
Show package contents 
Browse to "Trapcode Suite 12.0.0.mpkg"
Copy this and put it somewhere else (that's what I did maybe you can skip that step)
Right click and open this file with disk utility. Now you can create a DMG file and open. Worked for me.
Gods damn; how come nobody's gotten a Master Suite Key for any of these suites?  One serial to unlock them all, instead of C&Ping several.
